{"about_the_game":"<strong><i>What do you do when the Hero is Dead?</i></strong><br><br><strong>Final Winter</strong> is a Roguelite RPG with Speedrunning elements where the everyday common folk of a wretched little hamlet must confront a curse that, if not stopped, will kill within 10 minutes.<br><br><i>Anyone can be chosen at any time. </i> <br><br>Battle abominable horrors of the cave, loot precious lifesaving gear, and decide who will make the charge, and who will pave the way with their lives. The clock is ticking. Break the curse and save the village, lest this be your <strong>Final Winter!</strong><br><br><br><strong>Features:</strong><br><br>Play as one of 30 unique villagers summoned to defeat the dungeon and save the town. They each have their own small story to tell, given slowly through out the game. Be wary, for each villager only has 10 minutes to defeat the dungeon before they are lost to it. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1497510/extras/Dialogue_resize.png?t=1676436855\" /><br><br>Gather randomized items throughout the dungeon, deciding to either use them on the current run, or to send them back to town to help the next villager summoned. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1497510/extras/Found_item_resize.png?t=1676436855\" /><br><br>Gain crystals from monsters and floating crystal chests to permanently power up all future villagers. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1497510/extras/Gain_Crystals_resize.png?t=1676436855\" /><br><br>Defeat bosses to permanently unlock magical powers that add extra damage to combat and give you abilities to travel through the dungeon faster, all at the cost of mana.  <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1497510/extras/ice_dash_resize.png?t=1676436855